statements: SELECT * FROM workout_logs;
SELECT exercise_name, sets_completed, reps_completed FROM workout_logs WHERE sets_completed >= 3;
SELECT log_id, exercise_name, weight_lifted FROM workout_logs WHERE weight_lifted > 50;
SELECT exercise_name, reps_completed FROM workout_logs WHERE reps_completed < 10 ORDER BY exercise_name;
SELECT * FROM workout_logs WHERE exercise_name LIKE '%squat%' AND weight_lifted BETWEEN 80 AND 100 ORDER BY weight_lifted DESC;
SELECT * FROM workout_logs WHERE sets_completed > 3 ORDER BY reps_completed DESC, weight_lifted ASC
SELECT exercise_name, sets_completed FROM workout_logs WHERE weight_lifted <= 50
SELECT log_id, exercise_name, weight_lifted FROM workout_logs WHERE sets_completed = 3 AND reps_completed >= 10
SELECT exercise_name, SUM(weight_lifted) AS total_weight_lifted FROM workout_logs GROUP BY exercise_name
SELECT * FROM workout_logs WHERE reps_completed < 15 ORDER BY log_id DESC
SELECT * FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT exercise_name, sets, reps FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE weight > 50;
SELECT log_id, user_id, log_date FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE exercise_name = 'Squats';
SELECT * FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE log_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT username, join_date FROM Users ORDER BY join_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE sets > 3 ORDER BY log_date DESC, reps ASC
SELECT user_id, exercise_name, sets FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE weight >= 50 ORDER BY exercise_name
SELECT * FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE user_id = 1 AND log_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28' AND reps % 2 = 0
SELECT u.username, w.exercise_name, w.sets FROM Users u LEFT JOIN WorkoutLogs w ON u.user_id = w.user_id
SELECT u.username, COUNT(w.log_id) AS total_logs FROM Users u LEFT JOIN WorkoutLogs w ON u.user_id = w.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING total_logs > 5 ORDER BY total_logs DESC

SELECT log_id, user_id, exercise, sets, reps, weight FROM workout_logs WHERE user_id = 2 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT * FROM users WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT username, email FROM users ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT user_id, username, registration_date FROM users ORDER BY registration_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT log_id, exercise, sets, reps, weight, date FROM workout_logs WHERE user_id = 1001 ORDER BY date ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT log_id, user_id, progress_notes, progress_date FROM progress_tracking WHERE user_id = 2001 ORDER BY progress_date DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE username LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY username ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT log_id, exercise, sets, weight, date FROM workout_logs WHERE sets >= 3 AND weight >= 50 ORDER BY weight DESC, date ASC LIMIT 7

SELECT exercise_name, muscle_group FROM Exercises WHERE difficulty_level = 'Intermediate';

SELECT log_id, workout_date, exercise_name, sets_completed, reps_completed FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE sets_completed > 10;

SELECT * FROM WorkoutLogs;
SELECT exercise_name, sets_completed, reps_completed FROM WorkoutLogs WHERE workout_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY workout_date DESC;

SELECT Users.username, Progress.overall_performance_score, Progress.comments FROM Users JOIN Progress ON Users.user_id = Progress.user_id WHERE Users.age > 30 AND Progress.overall_performance_score > 8;
SELECT Exercises.exercise_name, Exercises.muscle_group, Progress.date_completed FROM Exercises JOIN Progress ON Exercises.exercise_id = Progress.log_id ORDER BY Progress.date_completed DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT Users.username, Users.age, Progress.comments, WorkoutLogs.sets_completed FROM Users JOIN Progress ON Users.user_id = Progress.user_id JOIN WorkoutLogs ON Progress.log_id = WorkoutLogs.log_id WHERE Users.weight < 70 AND WorkoutLogs.reps_completed < 10;
